sentence: list the flights that arrive and depart from general mitchell international airport
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v0.flight_id||'"', '"'||v0.to_airport||'"',
 '"'||v0.from_airport||'"' FROM flight v0 
WHERE ((v0.to_airport IN (
SELECT v1.airport_code FROM airport v1 
WHERE (v1.airport_code = 'MKE'))) OR (v0.from_airport IN (
SELECT v2.airport_code FROM airport v2 
WHERE (v2.airport_code = 'MKE'))));
